---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy — Pholio"
  description="Pholio collects the minimum necessary to run a publication and an app. No data selling, no third-party advertising, no cross-site tracking."
  lang="en"
  schemaType="WebSite"
>
  <section class="max-page ptitle">
    <nav class="crumb"><a href="/">PHOLIO</a><span class="sep">→</span><span class="cur">PRIVACY</span></nav>
    <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-top:24px">Effective 01 Jan 2026</div>
    <h1 class="hero-h1" style="margin-top:16px">Privacy.</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="max-page" style="padding-bottom:96px">
    <div class="max-prose prose-ed">
      <p class="drop-cap">Pholio collects the minimum necessary to run a publication and an app. We do not sell data, do not serve third-party advertising, and do not track you across the internet. This page explains what we do collect and why.</p>

      <h2>1. On this website</h2>
      <p>We use privacy-respecting analytics (Plausible) that records aggregate page views without cookies. We do not know who you are, where you browsed before, or what you do after you leave.</p>

      <h2>2. In the Pholio app</h2>
      <p>Creating an account is optional. If you create one, we store your email address and a hashed password. We store the list of answers you've saved offline so we can sync them between your devices.</p>

      <h2>3. Ask-a-local submissions</h2>
      <p>When you submit a question through the app or this website, we store the question, your email (if provided), and the reply you receive. We never publish your email or identifying information without explicit written consent.</p>

      <h2>4. Payments</h2>
      <p>App subscriptions are processed by Apple and Google. We never see your card or payment details.</p>

      <h2>5. Your rights</h2>
      <p>You can export or delete all data we hold about you from inside the app, or by writing to <a href="mailto:privacy@pholio.co">privacy@pholio.co</a>. Requests are actioned within 30 days.</p>

      <h2>6. Data retention</h2>
      <p>Account data is kept as long as your account is active and deleted 90 days after you close it. Anonymised analytics are kept for 24 months.</p>

      <h2>7. Changes</h2>
      <p>We'll email you before any material change to this policy. Minor edits (grammar, clarifications) appear in the changelog at the bottom of this page.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
